Times on the text agenda are shown in Philadelphia local time, UTC -4.

To see information on public side meetings, visit the meeting wiki. General meeting information is available on the meeting page of the IETF website.
For our social/hallway space, please visit Gather. Password: notewell
For more information on Meetecho, see our guides for Chairs and Participants.
